data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Aubrey!  This exquisite 4-bed, 3.5-bath Meritage home is nestled on a corner lot in master-planned Arrowbrooke within the Denton ISD.   Step inside to discover a dedicated office, perfect for remote work or quiet study time.  As you continue, you're greeted first by a dedicated dining space, then by a chef's dream of a kitchen that seamlessly flows into the breakfast area and spacious living room.  With the added convenience of a powder room, this space is an entertainer's dream!  The downstairs Owner's Retreat features an ensuite bath and a generously sized walk-in closet, offering a perfect sanctuary for relaxation.  Venture upstairs to find both a media room and a game room, along with 3 more bedrooms and 2 full baths.  This home has been thoughtfully refreshed with a new coat of paint, and with its 3-car garage, energy-efficient features, and Smart home system, it won't last!
